trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de elementos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" /> defines the allowable child content of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Span" />, and <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" /> define o conteúdo filho permitido dos elementos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Span" /> e <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> creation is only permitted inside an element that owns an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection>, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> or a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> criação só é permitida dentro de um elemento que possui um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection>, como um <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> ou <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph>.

trans-unit.source: As such, an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> cannot be instantiated directly and has no default or overloaded constructor.
trans-unit.target: Como tal, um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> não pode ser instanciado diretamente e não possui padrão ou sobrecarregado construtor.

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> element to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Text set as the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.Run.Text" /> property for the implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" />.
trans-unit.target: Texto definido como a propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.Run.Text" /> para o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> implícito.

trans-unit.source: Adds an implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> element with the given text, supplied as a <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> implícito com o texto especificado, fornecido como um <see cref="T:System.String" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> set as the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer.Child" /> property for the implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> definido como a propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer.Child" /> para o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" /> implícito.

trans-unit.source: Adds an implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" /> with the supplied <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> already in it.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" /> implícito com o <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> fornecido já nele.

trans-unit.source: Gets the first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o primeiro elemento de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> dentro desta instância de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: A primeira <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> elemento dentro desta instância do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the last <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o último elemento de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> dentro desta instância de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The last <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: A última <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> elemento dentro desta instância do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
